mutation ($payload:AdminCreateLangInput!)
{

		id
		name

		dir
		sort
		isActive
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminGetLangs (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminFindLang (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	adminFindLangById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		dir
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

	{

		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf

		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)

}

}
